\fB\-\-skip\-sys\-schema\fR
By default,
\fBmysql_upgrade\fR
installs the
sys
schema if it is not installed, and upgrades it to the current version otherwise\&. The
\fB\-\-skip\-sys\-schema\fR
option suppresses this behavior\&.
.RE
.sp
