\fB\-\-version\-check\fR,
\fB\-k\fR
Check the version of the server to which
\fBmysql_upgrade\fR
is connecting to verify that it is the same as the version for which
\fBmysql_upgrade\fR
was built\&. If not,
\fBmysql_upgrade\fR
exits\&. This option is enabled by default; to disable the check, use
\fB\-\-skip\-version\-check\fR\&.
.RE
